418
00:27:22,307 --> 00:27:23,516
I killed him.

419
00:27:24,017 --> 00:27:25,226
I stabbed him.

420
00:27:27,062 --> 00:27:29,064
Is this the answer you were looking for?

421
00:27:31,649 --> 00:27:34,277
Is there no other way
than admitting to a false charge

