to your question is...

465
00:29:58,129 --> 00:30:00,632
Yes, Bong-hui killed him.

466
00:30:01,257 --> 00:30:03,718
It's based on my personal feelings

467
00:30:04,052 --> 00:30:05,553
and reasonable doubts.

