00:30:07,847 --> 00:30:09,724
I didn't know
this is how you thought of her.

469
00:30:10,517 --> 00:30:12,477
I'm letting this take its own course,

470
00:30:13,645 --> 00:30:14,687
but one day,

471
00:30:15,271 --> 00:30:17,690
I'm definitely going to catch her.

